### 岗位类型管理 Inner API 测试
### mall-agent 服务内部接口（供 Feign 调用）
### 基础URL: {{baseUrl}}/inner/api/v1

# ============================================
# 1. 岗位类型列表查询
# ============================================

### 1.1 查询所有岗位类型（默认分页）
POST {{baseUrl}}/inner/api/v1/job-types/list
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "pageNum": 1,
  "pageSize": 10
}

### 1.2 按关键词搜索岗位类型
POST {{baseUrl}}/inner/api/v1/job-types/list
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "keyword": "销售",
  "pageNum": 1,
  "pageSize": 10
}

### 1.3 分页查询（第二页）
POST {{baseUrl}}/inner/api/v1/job-types/list
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "pageNum": 2,
  "pageSize": 5
}

# ============================================
# 2. 创建岗位类型
# ============================================

### 2.1 创建销售岗位类型
# @sql: sql/fixtures/job-type/init.sql
POST {{baseUrl}}/inner/api/v1/job-types/create
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "销售顾问",
  "code": "SALES",
  "description": "负责商品销售和客户维护",
  "sortOrder": 1,
  "operatorId": 1
}

### 2.2 创建技术岗位类型
POST {{baseUrl}}/inner/api/v1/job-types/create
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "技术工程师",
  "code": "TECH",
  "description": "负责技术开发和系统维护",
  "sortOrder": 2,
  "operatorId": 1
}

### 2.3 创建客服岗位类型
POST {{baseUrl}}/inner/api/v1/job-types/create
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "客服专员",
  "code": "CS",
  "description": "负责客户服务和投诉处理",
  "sortOrder": 3,
  "operatorId": 1
}

### 2.4 创建岗位类型（最小参数）
POST {{baseUrl}}/inner/api/v1/job-types/create
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "测试岗位",
  "code": "TEST"
}

### 2.5 创建岗位类型（编码已存在-预期失败）
POST {{baseUrl}}/inner/api/v1/job-types/create
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "重复编码测试",
  "code": "SALES",
  "operatorId": 1
}

### 2.6 创建岗位类型（名称空-预期失败）
POST {{baseUrl}}/inner/api/v1/job-types/create
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "",
  "code": "INVALID"
}

### 2.7 创建岗位类型（编码格式错误-预期失败）
POST {{baseUrl}}/inner/api/v1/job-types/create
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "格式错误测试",
  "code": "invalid-code"
}

# ============================================
# 3. 更新岗位类型
# ============================================

### 3.1 更新岗位类型信息
PUT {{baseUrl}}/inner/api/v1/job-types/update
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "id": 1,
  "name": "高级销售顾问",
  "description": "负责大客户销售和团队管理",
  "sortOrder": 1,
  "operatorId": 1
}

### 3.2 更新岗位类型（ID不存在-预期失败）
PUT {{baseUrl}}/inner/api/v1/job-types/update
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "id": 99999,
  "name": "不存在的岗位",
  "operatorId": 1
}

### 3.3 更新岗位类型（名称为空-预期失败）
PUT {{baseUrl}}/inner/api/v1/job-types/update
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "id": 1,
  "name": "",
  "operatorId": 1
}

# ============================================
# 4. 状态变更（启用/禁用）
# ============================================

### 4.1 禁用岗位类型
PUT {{baseUrl}}/inner/api/v1/job-types/status
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "id": 1,
  "status": 0,
  "operatorId": 1
}

### 4.2 启用岗位类型
PUT {{baseUrl}}/inner/api/v1/job-types/status
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "id": 1,
  "status": 1,
  "operatorId": 1
}

### 4.3 状态变更（无效状态值-预期失败）
PUT {{baseUrl}}/inner/api/v1/job-types/status
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "id": 1,
  "status": 99,
  "operatorId": 1
}

### 4.4 状态变更（ID不存在-预期失败）
PUT {{baseUrl}}/inner/api/v1/job-types/status
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "id": 99999,
  "status": 0,
  "operatorId": 1
}

# ============================================
# 5. 删除岗位类型
# ============================================

### 5.1 删除岗位类型
# @sql-cleanup: sql/fixtures/job-type/cleanup.sql
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/inner/api/v1/job-types/delete?id=3&operatorId=1

### 5.2 删除岗位类型（ID不存在-预期失败）
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/inner/api/v1/job-types/delete?id=99999&operatorId=1

### 5.3 删除岗位类型（已删除-预期失败）
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/inner/api/v1/job-types/delete?id=3&operatorId=1

# ============================================
# 6. 完整业务流程测试
# ============================================

### 6.1 创建 -> 查询 -> 更新 -> 禁用 -> 删除
### 步骤1：创建新岗位类型
POST {{baseUrl}}/inner/api/v1/job-types/create
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "临时测试岗位",
  "code": "TEMP001",
  "description": "用于测试完整流程",
  "sortOrder": 99,
  "operatorId": 1
}

### 步骤2：查询列表确认创建成功
POST {{baseUrl}}/inner/api/v1/job-types/list
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "keyword": "TEMP001",
  "pageNum": 1,
  "pageSize": 10
}

### 步骤3：更新岗位类型（使用实际返回的ID）
PUT {{baseUrl}}/inner/api/v1/job-types/update
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "id": 4,
  "name": "更新后的测试岗位",
  "description": "已更新描述",
  "sortOrder": 100,
  "operatorId": 1
}

### 步骤4：禁用岗位类型
PUT {{baseUrl}}/inner/api/v1/job-types/status
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "id": 4,
  "status": 0,
  "operatorId": 1
}

### 步骤5：删除岗位类型
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/inner/api/v1/job-types/delete?id=4&operatorId=1
